org.jhove2.module.format.gzip
Class GzipModule

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.module.AbstractModule
          org.jhove2.module.format.BaseFormatModule
              org.jhove2.module.format.gzip.GzipModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reportable, FormatModule, Parser, Validator, Module
@Persistent
public class GzipModule
extends BaseFormatModule
implements Validator

JHOVE2 GZip module. This module parses and validates GZip files in compliance with RFC 1952 (GZIP file format specification version 4.3) and supports multiple member GZIP files.

Author:
lbihanic, selghissassi, nicl
